ELO Diagnostic Seed
Starting every student at ELO 1000 wastes the first 10-15 session turns recalibrating difficulty. Use a 5-question diagnostic at onboarding to seed the ELO correctly:

def seed_elo_from_diagnostic(pct_correct: float) -> int:
    # 5 questions, results map to ELO band
    if pct_correct >= 0.80: return 1200   # advanced
    if pct_correct >= 0.60: return 1000   # grade-level
    if pct_correct >= 0.40: return 800    # needs support
    return 600                            # foundational gaps
 
# Questions generated from Chapter 1 of uploaded textbook
# Mix: 2 easy, 2 medium, 1 hard MCQs
# Student sees: 'Quick check — helps us personalise your experience'

