AWS S3 + CloudFront CDN — textbooks, reports, behavior photos in separate buckets with separate retention policies.
Task Queue
Celery workers on ECS Fargate — separate service, scales independently based on queue depth.
Monitoring
Sentry (errors + performance) + AWS CloudWatch (infra) + Grafana dashboard for business metrics.
SSL
AWS Certificate Manager (ACM) — auto-renewing TLS. CloudFront handles HTTPS termination.

