Security Hardening Checklist
    • All API endpoints require auth — run automated scan with OWASP ZAP
    • Cross-student data access impossible via RLS + tested with two separate accounts
    • Rate limiting on /auth/login (5 attempts per minute) to prevent brute force
    • Presigned S3 URLs expire in 1 hour — verify with expired URL request
    • All secrets in AWS Secrets Manager — nothing hardcoded, nothing in git
    • CORS whitelist: only your Vercel domain — no wildcard origins
    • WebSocket auth: token validated on handshake, not just on first message

Load Testing Checklist
    • 50 concurrent WebSocket sessions — CPU and memory stay under 70%
    • 100 concurrent PDF uploads — Celery queue drains within 5 minutes
    • 1000 simultaneous dashboard loads — Redis cache hit rate above 95%
    • Pinecone query latency under 100ms at 50 concurrent queries





